t pour qui ?<\/h3>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]Les personnes de plus de 60 ans, seules ou en couple, autonomes (ou en perte d\u2019autonomie accompagn\u00e9e au domicile), \u00e0 revenus modestes ou moyens.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h3>Les points cl\u00e9s<\/h3>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column]  <div class=\"in-skin-blocks-key-points\">\n    <div class=\"in-skin-blocks-key-points-content\">\n                              <div class=\"columns column-1 vc_col-xs-6 vc_col-sm-6 vc_col-md-3 vc_col-lg-3 \">\n          <div class=\"content\">\n                          <p class=\"in-skin-blocks-key-points-illustration\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"165\" height=\"213\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/picto-appart@3x.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/picto-appart@3x.png 165w, https:\/\/www.areli.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/picto-appart@3x-85x110.png 85w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 165px) 100vw, 165px\" \/><\/p>\n                                      <p class=\"in-skin-blocks-key-points-description\">T2 et T3 fonctionnels et confortables, avec des am\u00e9nagements adapt\u00e9s \u00e0 l\u2019avanc\u00e9e en \u00e2ge<\/p>\n                      <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                              <div class=\"columns column-1 vc_col-xs-6 vc_col-sm-6 vc_col-md-3 vc_col-lg-3 \">\n          <div class=\"content\">\n                          <p class=\"in-skin-blocks-key-points-illustration\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"165\" height=\"213\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/picto-apl@3x.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/picto-apl@3x.png 165w, https:\/\/www.areli.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/picto-apl@3x-85x110.png 85w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 165px) 100vw, 165px\" \/><\/p>\n                                      <p class=\"in-skin-blocks-key-points-description\">Co\u00fbt loyer + charges + services adapt\u00e9 aux revenus moyens et modestes<\/p>\n                      <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                              <div class=\"columns column-1 vc_col-xs-6 vc_col-sm-6 vc_col-md-3 vc_col-lg-3 \">\n          <div class=\"content\">\n                          <p class=\"in-skin-blocks-key-points-illustration\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"165\" height=\"213\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/picto-equipe@3x.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/picto-equipe@3x.png 165w, https:\/\/www.areli.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/picto-equipe@3x-85x110.png 85w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 165px) 100vw, 165px\" \/><\/p>\n                                      <p class=\"in-skin-blocks-key-points-description\">Pr\u00e9sence au quotidien d\u2019un responsable de r\u00e9sidence<\/p>\n                      <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                              <div class=\"columns column-1 vc_col-xs-6 vc_col-sm-6 vc_col-md-3 vc_col-lg-3 \">\n          <div class=\"content\">\n                          <p class=\"in-skin-blocks-key-points-illustration\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"165\" height=\"213\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/picto-commerce@3x.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/picto-commerce@3x.png 165w, https:\/\/www.areli.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/picto-commerce@3x-85x110.png 85w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 165px) 100vw, 165px\" \/><\/p>\n                                      <p class=\"in-skin-blocks-key-points-description\">R\u00e9sidences situ\u00e9es en centre-ville, \u00e0 proximit\u00e9 des commerces, des services et des transports en commun<\/p>\n                      <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                                                <div class=\"columns column-1 vc_col-xs-6 vc_col-sm-6 vc_col